toElliptic

▸ toElliptic(): any

Defined in Signature.ts:38

Export Signature as elliptic-format Signature NOTE: This isn't an actual elliptic-format Signature, as ec.Signature is not exported by the library. That's also why the return type is any. We're actually returning an object with the 3 params not an ec.Signature. Further NOTE: @types/elliptic shows ec.Signature as exported; it is not. Hence the any.

Returns: any
